Valentine parasite.

530
00:29:27,862 --> 00:29:29,439
Nice work, Tony Hopkins.

531
00:29:29,564 --> 00:29:31,374
I stole it from the Lamda Sig house.

532
00:29:31,499 --> 00:29:34,171
All right, here.
Keep the change.

533
00:29:38,668 --> 00:29:40,450
Well, you look confident.

534
00:29:40,575 --> 00:29:42,446
