559
00:30:50,792 --> 00:30:51,848
It's just...

560
00:30:52,018 --> 00:30:55,561
The worst thing that ever has happened
to me, happened on Valentine's Day.

561
00:30:56,257 --> 00:30:58,361
God. It was so horrible.

562
00:30:58,486 --> 00:31:01,230
