Or go to parties.

579
00:32:00,971 --> 00:32:02,525
I got into Yale Law School.

580
00:32:02,650 --> 00:32:04,376
You must be excited.

581
00:32:05,119 --> 00:32:06,319
And terrified.

582
00:32:07,009 --> 00:32:10,166
I've lived my whole life for the
future at the expense of the present.

583
00:32:10,291 --> 00:32:14,291
So now I have to fit the entire
college experience into one semester.

584
00:32:14,562 --> 00:32:18,562
And I want to be more
than the geeky smart girl.

585
00:32:19,934 --> 00:32:22,219
- Is that sad ?
- Why do you think I rushed KT ?

586
00:32:22,344 --> 00:32:24,358
I want to be more than
the geeky smart girl, too.

587
00:32:25,330 --> 00:32:26,430
I mean, guy.

588
00:32:30,544 --> 00:32:34,090
