to find something beyond ZBZ.

590
00:32:37,749 --> 00:32:40,129
It's sweet of you to think of her.

591
00:32:40,254 --> 00:32:42,064
And though I'll never admit it,

592
00:32:42,189 --> 00:32:44,967
I think your sister's doing
a fine job of catching up.

593
00:32:45,173 --> 00:32:47,036
I guess we all have regrets.

594
00:32:48,183 --> 00:32:50,233
I don't think I'll regret this.

595
00:32:57,185 --> 00:33:00,476
