638
00:34:54,564 --> 00:34:57,802
I bet you'll never forget the first time
you were struck by Cupid's arrow.

639
00:34:58,001 --> 00:34:59,470
Actually it was Pickle's.

640
00:34:59,669 --> 00:35:00,872
