Have you seen him ?

650
00:35:40,176 --> 00:35:42,430
What's your problem ?
He's freaking beautiful.

651
00:35:42,612 --> 00:35:45,627
I know.
I just prefer my men handsome.

652
00:35:46,349 --> 00:35:47,766
