653
00:35:47,891 --> 00:35:50,865
When I came out that one week
I wanted to listen to Indigo Girls

654
00:35:50,990 --> 00:35:53,776
and wear no makeup. Grant's
experimenting with the lifestyle.

655
00:35:53,944 --> 00:35:56,194
- Big whoop. It's natural.
- So I'm overreacting ?

656
00:35:56,393 --> 00:35:58,520
You are a pretty uptight gay.
Lighten up.

657
00:35:58,645 --> 00:36:02,367
If you want it to work,
it's something you're gonna have to do.

658
00:36:02,535 --> 00:36:05,002
Or I could just buy him
a really fancy necklace.

659
00:36:05,127 --> 00:36:07,199
- Is that from Evan ?
- I've decided I like it.

660
00:36:07,324 --> 00:36:10,959
- It's a keepsake I can keep forever.
- I think that was his idea.

661
00:36:12,736 --> 00:36:15,005
Really ?
He said that ?

662
00:36:15,173 --> 00:36:16,323
