733
00:41:21,992 --> 00:41:23,104
Present. Get it ?

734
00:41:24,493 --> 00:41:25,852
OK. Me first.

735
00:41:32,444 --> 00:41:33,531
"Look up".

736
00:41:38,167 --> 00:41:39,967
Just what I always wanted.

737
00:41:40,791 --> 00:41:44,158
You were so right.
It's really hard to buy a gift.

738
00:41:44,283 --> 00:41:47,420
I totally cracked under the pressure.
You're off the hook from this day forward.

739
00:41:47,588 --> 00:41:48,880
Well, that's good.

740
00:41:49,812 --> 00:41:52,550
Because I don't think I could top
what I did this year.

741
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:54,904
Bringing me to the Quickie Mart ?

742
00:41:55,347 --> 00:41:56,928
It's not just any Quickie Mart.

743
00:41:57,601 --> 00:41:59,764
You and I came here once
freshman year for snacks.

744
00:42:00,142 --> 00:42:01,800
I thought it looked familiar.

745
00:42:01,979 --> 00:42:05,177
You were buying all this food
and I was wondering

746
00:42:05,302 --> 00:42:07,071
if you got high
when I wasn't looking.

747
00:42:07,196 --> 00:42:10,040
And when I asked you
about it, you said :

748
00:42:10,165 --> 00:42:12,110
"I want to stock the fridge
in your room",

749
00:42:12,235 --> 00:42:14,905
because you knew I was lazy
about going to the cafeteria

750
00:42:15,075 --> 00:42:17,115
and you didn't want me to go hungry.

751
00:42:18,128 --> 00:42:21,252
- Do you want food ?
- And you were at the register, paying.

752
00:42:21,377 --> 00:42:23,777
You tucked your hair
behind your ear,

753
00:42:24,536 --> 00:42:27,016
looked back at me and just...

754
00:42:28,639 --> 00:42:29,489
smiled.

755
00:42:35,057 --> 00:42:38,007
This is where I first realized
that I loved you.

756
00:42:38,882 --> 00:42:41,132
And I've loved you every day since.

757
00:42:45,854 --> 00:42:47,022
My God.

758
00:42:47,536 --> 00:42:48,607
That's my gift.

759
00:42:48,805 --> 00:42:50,405
My God.
It's perfect.

760
00:42:58,648 --> 00:42:59,545
So, I...

761
00:43:00,816 --> 00:43:03,516
- I guess I kinda won ?
- Yeah, you so won.

762
00:43:09,561 --> 00:43:10,311
Yes !

763
00:43:10,660 --> 00:43:12,460
Suck it, Valentine's Day !

